### Create or Update Meal
POST {{baseUrl}}/meals
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-01-20",
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 2,
  "note": "Extra spicy"
}

### Create Breakfast
POST {{baseUrl}}/meals
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-01-20",
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "count": 1
}

### Create Dinner
POST {{baseUrl}}/meals
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-01-20",
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Light meal"
}

### List All Meals
GET {{baseUrl}}/meals
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Meals by Date
GET {{baseUrl}}/meals?date=2024-01-20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Meals by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/meals?mealType=LUNCH
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Meals by Date and Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/meals?date=2024-01-20&mealType=LUNCH
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update Meal (replace :id with actual meal ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/meals/:id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "count": 3,
  "note": "Updated note"
}

### Cancel Meal (replace :id with actual meal ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/meals/:id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Meal Service Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/meals/health
